{"tid":1366131,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"《27/7》水邊村遊樂場 齊來做運動","createTime":"2019-07-26T01:07:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T01:07:27.000Z","uid":80234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cef2e0677806678f4d8472d0f66076688bda824c","tid":1366131,"uid":80234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:07:27.000Z","msg":"響應康文署全民運動日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yv521m9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYv521m9.png&h=f77c5f28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n身體機能衰退，冰封三尺，非一日之寒<br />\n<br />\n基於運動科學做運動前都要做熱身<br />\n<br />\n呼籲大家27/7為身體健康去做運動<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u6m5Zc4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu6m5Zc4.png&h=c4ec2fc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當日冇發出不反對通知書，水邊村球場冇集會，有場地做運動可以踢波<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 去7人足球場跟隊踢波嘅朋友請帶齊防護裝備，戴pad 保護自己合理啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Eo6BmsN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEo6BmsN.png&h=60aab9f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 踢完波去隔離元朗大球場訓練田徑，標槍推鉛球我唔識，接下棒練接力跑練氣<br />\n<br />\n帶短棒出街都人之常情？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yP0izSw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyP0izSw.png&h=5601a960&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 跑完步關節痛要遊水舒緩泳池就係隔離，戴副泳鏡防水防其他野<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/10ckOfo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F10ckOfo.png&h=7cb94dbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 元朗公園，平時有人踩單車跑步，去完水邊村遊樂場仲可以做咩運動大家自由發揮<br />\n<br />\n「日日運動半個鐘 健康快樂人輕鬆」為口號，鼓勵不同年齡和能力的市民<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">恆常參與</span></span></strong></span>活動，傳遞勤做運動有益身心，守護香港的訊息"}]}